metadata.title: Bathymetry of the Bering Strait - Chukota to Diomede Island

creators.name: U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), Alaska Biological Science Center, Marine

metadata.description: Bathymetric contours of the Russian side of the Bering Strait at 1:1,000,000 scale. Digitized from the "Topographic and Bathymetric Map of the Northern Bering Sea region" (USGS Prof. Paper 759-B, 1976)
metadata.notes:
